This is the README file for i18n, a Perl pragma for Internationalization.

Please type "perldoc i18n" after installation to see
the module usage information.

* Installation

i18n uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

